Farooq Kathwari is chairman,
          CEO and president of Ethan Allen Interiors Inc., a leading home furnishings
          manufacturer and retailer. In addition to overseeing this international
          corporation, he also lends his considerable leadership skills to humanitarian
          efforts, including working for human rights and developing international
          conflict resolutions. click
          here to read more... 




















