American born son of Ethan Allen furniture tycoon Farooq Kathwari, was killed fighting Jihad in Afghanistan: Farooq Kathwari was speaker at radical Islamist ISNA conference in 2004 - Militant Islam Monitor - Militant Islam Monitor



















