Individual




M. Farooq Kathwari



Mr. M. F. Kathwari is Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at Ethan Allen Interiors, Inc., a Director-Diplomacy Study Institute at Georgetown University, and Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at Ethan Allen Global, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at National Retail Federation, Refugees International, International Rescue Committee, Inc., and American Home Furnishings Alliance, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Kashmir and an MBA from New York University.



